title: Death Cab For Cutie - 2003 - Transatlanticism [FLAC]
description:
Transatlanticism is an album released in 2003 by Death Cab for Cutie. It is the band&#039;s fourth LP and eighth record release. The album peaked at number 97 on the Billboard 200 Album Chart and as of December 2005 it has sold 397,582 copies in the U.S. Tracks from Transatlanticism have been featured in several motion pictures and television shows, most notably FOX&#039;s The O.C. and HBO&#039;s Six Feet Under (?Transatlanticism?).
